    "description": "诡域 是一款多人合作 结合PVE与PVP的游戏，将带你进入惊悚诡异的未知世界<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/6aaef8b21308bc0cb2522f4d8811909f.poster.avif?t=1710408265\" width=606 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/6aaef8b21308bc0cb2522f4d8811909f.webm?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/6aaef8b21308bc0cb2522f4d8811909f.mp4?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>玩家必须齐心协力占领并保护他们的基地免受一波又一波可怕生物的袭击。但危险并不止于此——其他玩家也在试图占领同一个基地，所以你也需要抵挡他们！<br>随着游戏的进行，您需要占领更多的基地团队才能更好的维持生存。每个基地都有其独特的挑战和奖励，因此您需要谨慎选择策略。<br><br><strong>搜刮物資</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/c4eb49a0715134b14188c6efff2a336a.poster.avif?t=1710408265\" width=606 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/c4eb49a0715134b14188c6efff2a336a.webm?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/c4eb49a0715134b14188c6efff2a336a.mp4?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在这个世界中将会有不同类型的箱子、柜子，它们将要使用不同方法来打开。<br>你们需要齐心协力寻找资源，寻找武器和工具，你们可以选择不同的工作来帮助你们的团队，击退追杀你们的致命生物！<br><br><strong>世界時間事件</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/7d7c9db625fa93460a67f9c8424bc8c4.poster.avif?t=1710408265\" width=606 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/7d7c9db625fa93460a67f9c8424bc8c4.webm?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/7d7c9db625fa93460a67f9c8424bc8c4.mp4?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>这个世界有4个季节，中央的建筑在晚上会呈现出不同的颜色来表示季节。<br>在不同的季节，会有不同事件，如万圣节、圣诞节和新年烟花。<br><br><strong>天气</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/9728b2c4d520e4c6b584b387c28624b0.poster.avif?t=1710408265\" width=606 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/9728b2c4d520e4c6b584b387c28624b0.webm?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/9728b2c4d520e4c6b584b387c28624b0.mp4?t=1710408265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>天气变幻莫测。每个季节都会带来一组独特的天气条件。<br>它还对游戏玩法产生了切实的影响。某些生物或生物可能只在特定的天气条件下出现，为玩家提供了新的挑战和奖励。<br><br><br>因此，召集您的团队，准备抵御一切困难保卫您的基地。未知的世界等着你的到来!<br>不要忘记关注并添加到您的愿望清单^ ^<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167390/extras/75a3ce09c153d93269d1ea6f5fb92f69.avif?t=1710408265\" width=606 height=150 /></span>",
